Hey, Twilight! Pinkie Pie started
Pin the Tail on the Pony. Wanna play?

17:54.931 --> 18:00.094
No! All the ponies in this town are CRAZY!
Do you know what time it is?

18:00.199 --> 18:02.415
It's the eve of the Summer Sun Celebration.

18:02.416 --> 18:05.755
Everypony has to stay up or they'll
miss the Princess raise the sun.

18:05.826 --> 18:09.679
You really should lighten up Twilight.
It's a party!

18:12.794 --> 18:15.869
Here I thought I'd have time to learn
more about the Elements of Harmony.

18:15.881 --> 18:20.246
But, silly me, all this ridiculous
friendmaking has kept me from it!

18:24.003 --> 18:26.842
"Legend has it that in the longest day
of the thousandth year..."

18:26.843 --> 18:31.044
"...the stars will aid in her escape and
she will bring about everlasting night."

18:32.348 --> 18:36.953
I hope the Princess was right.
I hope it really is just an old pony tale.

18:37.024 --> 18:39.496
Come on, Twilight!
It's time to watch the sun rise!

18:48.118 --> 18:49.383
Isn't this exciting?

