Fillies and gentlecolts.

19:05.604 --> 19:08.828
As mayor of Ponyville,
it is my great pleasure...

19:08.829 --> 19:12.788
...to announce the beginning
of the Summer Sun Celebration!

19:16.152 --> 19:20.438
In just a few moments our town will
witness the magic of the sunrise.

19:20.573 --> 19:24.103
And celebrate this, the longest day of the year!

19:24.715 --> 19:29.391
And now it is my great honor to
introduce to you the ruler of our land.

19:29.551 --> 19:32.982
The very pony, who gives us the sun
and the moon each and every day.

19:33.045 --> 19:37.728
The good, the wise, the bringer
of harmony to all of Equestria...

19:38.155 --> 19:38.842
Ready?

19:39.259 --> 19:41.362
...Princess Celestia!

19:46.244 --> 19:47.976
This can't be good.

19:48.821 --> 19:52.827
Remain calm, everypony.
There must be a reasonable explanation.

19:53.425 --> 19:55.813
I love guessing games! Is she hiding?

19:57.153 --> 19:58.505
She's gone!

20:01.809 --> 20:03.949
She's good!

20:07.953 --> 20:09.353
Oh no...

20:11.712 --> 20:13.532
Nightmare Moon!

20:15.089 --> 20:17.717
Oh, my beloved subjects!

20:17.868 --> 20:23.079
It's been so long since I've seen your
precious little sun-loving faces.

20:23.196 --> 20:25.334
What did you do with our Princess?!

20:25.730 --> 20:27.106
Whoa there, Nelly...!

20:29.147 --> 20:33.793
Why, am I not royal enough for you?
Don't you know who I am?

20:34.388 --> 20:35.380
More guessing games!

20:35.530 --> 20:38.722
Um... Pokey Smokes!
How about Queen Meanie?

20:38.723 --> 20:40.888
No! Black Snooty, Black Snooty...!

20:42.891 --> 20:48.276
Does my crown no longer count now that
I have been imprisoned for a thousand years?

20:48.347 --> 20:52.022
Did you not recall the legend?
Did you not see the signs?

20:52.051 --> 20:54.585
I did! And I know who you are!

20:54.586 --> 20:56.413
You're the Mare in the Moon.

20:56.414 --> 20:57.828
Nightmare Moon.

20:59.701 --> 21:03.211
Well well well. Somepony who remembers me.

21:03.212 --> 21:05.258
Then you also know why I'm here.

21:05.271 --> 21:07.547
You're here to... to...

21:10.840 --> 21:14.168
Remember this day, little ponies,
for it was your last.

21:14.446 --> 21:16.148
From this moment forth...

21:16.149 --> 21:19.503
THE NIGHT WILL LAST FOREVER!

